                <h3>ABOUT US</h3>

                <p>In a globalised economy characterised by constant change, a firm’s success is predicated on its
                    ability to adapt and evolve on a dime. Yet, the way businesses staff and hire has remained largely
                    unchanged over past decades. Exorbitant recruitment agency fees and prohibitive labour regulations
                    continue to haunt businesses. Hiring decisions have remained restricted to CVs and interviews, which
                    risks revealing more about a candidate’s tactical knowledge in navigating the application process
                    than their actual ability to perform the job </p>

                <p>TGC was founded by a team of young and driven recent graduates, determined to utilise our extensive
                    network and job hunting experience to deliver a more efficient and flexible recruitment solution.
                    Through the use of scalable technology, we aim to eliminate the inefficiencies of traditional
                    recruitment through enabling businesses to work in a more flexible manner.</p>

                <p>Our platform connects businesses with top graduate students for freelance work, allowing businesses
                    to hire through a flexible project based approach, depending on the skills and duration required and
                    budget available for each specific job. Firms may also use project based work as a means to trial
                    candidates before committing to a permanent hire. On the other hand, top graduate students can
                    discover and work on rewarding paid projects remotely on top of their studies, boosting their
                    professional experience and career prospects.</p>


